@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@clienteId = 2

##
## CRUD
##

### Get all
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes

### Get por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}

### Criar cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Jo√£ko da Silva",
    "email": "joako.silva@example.com"
}

### Atualizar cliente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Makria Souza",
    "email": "makria.souza@example.com"
}

### excluir cliente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}


##
## Saldo
##

### depositar valor
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/depositar
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "valor": 10
}

### saque de valor normal, deve funcionar
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/sacar
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "valor": 100
}

### valor maior que o saldo tem que dar erro
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/sacar
